text: Molokanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Yermolayevsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 338 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 17 km from Yermolayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Molokanovo
